# Portal colors

Reference for UI colors in the CRM web app. **Source of truth for runtime CSS:** `public/layouts/basic/skins/style.css` (base) and `public/layouts/basic/skins/twilight/style.css` (default user theme overrides). Edit source `.css`, then minify — see `css.mdc`.

When adding new UI, reuse these tokens instead of inventing one-off hex values.

## Accent (orange)

| Token | Value | Usage |
|---|---|---|
| **portal-orange** | `#EC971F` / `rgb(236, 151, 31)` | Autocomplete hover/focus row (`.ui-autocomplete.reference-ac .reference-ac-row`) — reference fields + global search |

## Blues (twilight theme)

| Token | Value | Usage |
|---|---|---|
| **portal-blue** | `#4979AA` | Twilight accent bar (`.infoUser`), active tab highlights |
| **portal-blue-dark** | `#3A6288` | Twilight blue hover / pressed state |

## Neutrals — dark chrome

| Token | Value | Usage |
|---|---|---|
| **portal-nav-bg** | `#2A2F35` | Left panel background |
| **portal-nav-hover** | `#404952` | Module menu item hover (header dropdown) |
| **portal-header-muted** | `#4A5364` | Header chrome, twilight checked checkboxes |

## Neutrals — text

| Token | Value | Usage |
|---|---|---|
| **portal-text** | `#2B2B2B` | Primary body text |
| **portal-text-secondary** | `#555555` | Section labels (e.g. autocomplete category headers) |
| **portal-text-muted** | `#777777` | Subtitles (`.reference-ac-subtitle`) |
| **portal-text-disabled** | `#888888` | Empty states, placeholder-like copy |
| **portal-text-on-dark** | `#FFFFFF` | Text/icons on dark header bars |

## Neutrals — surfaces & borders

| Token | Value | Usage |
|---|---|---|
| **portal-surface** | `#FFFFFF` | Cards, dropdowns, inputs |
| **portal-border** | `#DDDDDD` / `#DDD` | Standard borders, autocomplete frame |
| **portal-shadow** | `rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12)` | Dropdown box-shadow (reference-ac) |

## Legacy (avoid for new UI)

| Token | Value | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| **bootstrap-blue** | `#428BCA` | Old jQuery UI autocomplete focus; replaced by **portal-orange** in `.reference-ac` |

## Autocomplete (reference-ac)

Shared by reference fields (`ReferenceAutocomplete.js`) and global search (`Header.js` → `gsAutocomplete`):

- Menu: **portal-border**, **portal-shadow**, `border-radius: 6px`
- Row hover/focus background: **portal-orange**
- Subtitle text: **portal-text-muted**
- Category header: **portal-text-secondary**, `font-size: 12px`, `font-weight: 600`
- Match highlight: inherit color/weight (no yellow `mark` background)

See also: `listview-javascript-playbook.mdc`, `detailview-javascript-playbook.mdc` (field widgets); `css.mdc` (minification).
